  <brief_title>To Demonstrate the Superior Efficacy of NYC 0462 Ointment Over That of the Placebo in the Treatment of Plaque Psoriasis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Randomized, Vehicle-controlled, Parallel-Group Study Comparing NYC-0462 Ointment To a Vehicle Control</official_title>
