  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this trial is to assess the efficacy of NYC-0462 Ointment in the Treatment of
      Plaque Psoriasis.Treatment medication will be administered as follows: A thin layer of study
      product will be applied to the affected skin, excluding the face, once daily, at
      approximately the same time daily.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
