  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of stable, symptomatic plaque psoriasis

          -  Good health with the exception of psoriasis

          -  % BSA and plaque elevation requirements

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects who are pregnant, nursing or planning a pregnancy within the study
             participation period.

          -  Subjects who have any systemic or dermatological disorders with the exception of
             psoriasis
